  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Tiotropium in Patients With COPD and Concomitant Diagnosis of Asthma</brief_title>
  <official_title>A 12-week Randomised, Double Blind, Placebo Controlled, Parallel Group Trial Evaluating the Efficacy and Safety of Inhaled Tiotropium 18Î¼g q.d. in Patients With COPD and a Concomitant Diagnosis of Asthma</official_title>
